com.soebes.subversion.sapm
Class AccessRulesDerivingPermissionsTest

java.lang.Object
  com.soebes.subversion.sapm.AccessRulesDerivingPermissionsTest

public class AccessRulesDerivingPermissionsTest
extends Object

This test will check if the given users and group members do have the correct access permissions within the different folders and/or repositories. 

 [groups]
 developer = harry, brian
 admin = micheal
 [/]
 * =
 [repository:/test/trunk]
 @developer = r
 @admin = rw
The tests will check if the AccessLevel will be extracted correctly and furthermore if the access to different directories inside this repository will work well.

Author:
Karl Heinz Marbaise
